Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:04.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}FLYING IN THE SKY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:09.19,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最高的地方 馳騁於空中的任何角落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:10.92,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.90,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀著光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:16.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮大地的盡頭呼喚奇跡的咒語 {\fnComic Sans MS}SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.78,0:00:25.44,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不遲疑的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:31.72,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有無限的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:39.08,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論嘗試多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:47.51,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多麼痛苦都貫徹到底{\fnComic Sans MS}（G GUNDAM）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.57,0:00:50.63,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛隨時都充斥於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:54.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:57.32,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雙手 咆哮著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:01:01.31,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向明天飛奔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.40,0:01:03.10,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}BRIGHT YOU NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:08.06,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所描繪的未來之藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.80,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS}SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:11.60,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.34,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部如你所願 {\fnComic Sans MS}I GET A CHANCE！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請容我講解GUNDAM FIGHT的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那起源自60年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開被極度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.22,0:01:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛上宇宙的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免衛星國家之間爆發全面戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是創立每四年一度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國派出代表的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操縱名為GUNDAM的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以FIGHT的方式不斷戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後勝出的GUNDAM代表的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能得到衛星國家聯邦的主導權
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然創出充滿體育精神的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，剩下的問題有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項FIGHT的舞台是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，就是我們居住的被極度污染的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.93,0:02:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，今屆大賽看來有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的人，你有見過這男人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.21,0:02:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片會掀起多猛烈的戰鬥風暴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日的對手是neo Russia的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bolt Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞Fighter是個PRISONER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，GUNDAM FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs56}大逃亡！被囚禁的Gundam Fighter！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，不知從什麼時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一帶稱為GUNDAM墳場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入市內的GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會消失得無影無蹤，不會再出現
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙·卡休？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒講過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.66,0:03:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般遊客不會有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這種有監獄的市鎮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，多蒙的確來了這市鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM墳場？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？他們為何在找GUNDAM？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講！你的真正身份是GUNDAM Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裡是找neo Russia的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…講過很多次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一般的遊客啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還狡辯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快講出你的GUNDAM在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙只是在市內四處遊蕩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，聽聞他在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠那些證據也不可證明他是Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我們的情報網是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人一定是neo Japan的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些國家名是什麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，告訴我，這男人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我解開手銬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快替他治療
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.97,0:05:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手便會廢掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片我收回了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣便行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？那班人有何目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人…即使怎樣掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能逃離這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像同樣是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可惜我不能在這種地方浪費時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙我的統統給我滾開！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的拳勁…無效！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事要問那男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且，我也要你規矩一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯哥·加魯斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，即使不能插手外國的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，我們也…拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，我再多觀察一會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙那傢伙，總是要我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寧願跟他絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙…多蒙·卡休
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？那怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點捉住他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後，把那部Devil Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，只有那方法才可救到他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才能救他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看來做了很可怕的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還是徹底死心比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一被關進這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍…人生便完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Fighter先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我巴杜文大爺也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每四年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會有你這類人被關進這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，他們會都跌進陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那班人發放消息說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.98,0:08:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Russia的GUNDAM在那市鎮裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把每一個來到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵國的Fighter捉住，關進這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此，neo Russia便不戰而勝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被隔離在這個任何通訊方法也無效的島上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國的人便無法插手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外界永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你估計被囚的Fighter會有何下場？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要在這裡拚命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群被囚的喪家犬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，不可以輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM Fighter變成這樣便完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,neo Russia的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用這種方法收集各國的最新科技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用來製造GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該很強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會成功吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派我們的Fighter混入囚犯裡做間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後令他說出GUNDAM藏在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得真周到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，從另一角度看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.01,0:10:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是天堂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，在大賽中失蹤的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是國家的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裡後也只會被追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是，你也是其中一個Fighter？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.49,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別胡說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一般罪犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是快點說出GUNDAM的所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！那傢伙做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，站在那裡不要動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好，放我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著，明天工作結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來我身邊，一起離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守衛比想像中更加深嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不能查明多蒙是否在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海上又不能把核戰車交給他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你也不知死活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去，你會沒命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點說出GUNDAM的所在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外，你想離開這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為多謝你照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起走好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你說什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎樣逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你能偷一部車回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出去便會掉進海裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行不通啊，行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點放棄你的GUNDAM吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚好冷啊，好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.23,0:12:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？那男人有所行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，只靠那點情報
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.70,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不知他何時會逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人在打什麼主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣？你走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和這些雀鳥分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講，你想怎樣逃走？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要令這些…能源管爆炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救火！快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛隊！囚犯逃獄呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣衝出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正面不行啊！怎辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結冰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日的寒冷天氣令湖結冰了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了！我自由了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自由了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙的反應恢復了，好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙竟然逃走！他有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bolt Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，由我這裡遠程控制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差少許便能去到市鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，看來不能輕易到達
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，它來得太快了，難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！我沒通風報訊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先阻止他們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那傢伙是間諜嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為什麼…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.66,0:16:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上來！是核戰車啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你，莉茵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.60,0:16:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧！Shining Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是neo Japan的Shining Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來阿魯哥想和這傢伙決鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝逃獄引敵人的GUNDAM出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好，剩下的交給我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓任何人妨礙我戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT，準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…GUNDAM FIGHT！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星鎚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我一起向你和那鐵球報恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太…！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.51,0:18:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的頭竟能承受多蒙的拳勁！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看neo Russia的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿魯哥，毀掉它的頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.66,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？這就完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監獄裡那場架只是虛有其表嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也只有這點技倆嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭是我的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油！年輕人！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這隻手在閃耀和咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它在叫我打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHINING FINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是打和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯…我不能戰鬥下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人，阿魯哥·加魯斯基
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的拳裡感到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監獄的囚犯所沒有的Fighter靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是想跟你決鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他因此而逃獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以前是個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處搶掠衛星的宇宙海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽聞他參加今屆大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了換取同伴的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝在他胸膛的炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換言之他永遠是個囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一剩下的自由只有戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我不認識這男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今後有何打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過你們剛才的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也記起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個放棄了自由的Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會繼續逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至再次得到自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，別忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM FIGHT國際條約第七條
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球是擂台
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們身為Fighter的一日在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也和他一樣是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我也是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個名為地球的擂台的囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.40,0:22:32.00,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便數千的日夜流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.39,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所到達的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:40.83,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨著 追求著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.30,0:22:44.40,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫步著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.64,0:22:51.55,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人啊 在我瞳孔的深處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:57.25,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實搖曳著的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:02.56,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何傳達才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.58,0:23:09.04,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓受傷的心與身體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:13.22,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這溫暖的懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.35,0:23:19.21,Song_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比海更深沉的睡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遣送回neo Japan殖民衛星的多蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.92,0:23:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他的是可怕的測試
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.34,0:23:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片上的男人究竟是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.61,0:23:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為最強最惡的Devil Gundam又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多蒙真正的目的現在水落石出了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 機動武鬥傳G GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥吧多蒙！地球就是擂台！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,READY GO！


